  "text": "DNA-binding proteins have been implicated in trans interactions in chromosomes in multiple studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] . It would be interesting to determine the identity of protein X, which could be responsible for the effect that we observed. ",
